description         The CLI for PRQL, a modern language for transforming data
long_description    {*}{
    PRQL is a modern language for transforming data — a simple, powerful, pipelined SQL
    replacement. Like SQL, it's readable, explicit and declarative. Unlike SQL, it forms
    a logical pipeline of transformations, and supports abstractions such as variables and
    functions. It can be used with any database that uses SQL, since it compiles to SQL.
}

installs_libs       no
use_configure       no
